title: Second Floor Unit for July 1, Balcony, Open Floor Plan, Parking, A/C
posting_body: ['Second Floor Unit w/Balcony Available July 1, Open Floor Plan, Ample Off-Street Parking', 'Property Address', '2008 S 4th St - #2E | South St. Paul, MN 55075', 'Available: 07/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do showings once an application is approved.', ' To apply, go to <URL>  Each adult would apply and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Second floor unit available July 1 in South St. Paul.', ' All carpeting was just installed last year.', ' Large living room with a walk out to the balcony.', 'Small dining area is open to the living room and connected to the kitchen.', 'Kitchen has an oven/range, refrigerator and microwave.', 'Large bedroom with a walk-in closet.', 'Off-street parking is included at this building.', "Garages are $50/month, but they're all currently rented.", 'Large side yard at the building.', 'Laundry on every floor.', 'Rent includes water, trash and gas (heat).', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Cats are okay with $25/month pet fee per.', 'Sorry no dogs.', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 630', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $900.00', 'Available: 07/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $900.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
